<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN216">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kēṭṭaṉ māttirai yalla tiyāvatuṅ</l>
<l>kāṇṭa lillā tiyāṇṭupala kaḻiya</l>
<l>vaḻuviṉṟu paḻakiya kiḻamaiya rāyiṉu</l>
<l>maritē tōṉṟa lataṉpaṭa voḻukaleṉ</l>
<l>ṟaiyaṅ koḷḷaṉmi ṉāraṟi vāḷī</l>
<l>rikaḻvila ṉiṉiya ṉiyātta naṇpiṉaṉ</l>
<l>pukaḻkeṭa varūum poyvēṇ ṭalaṉē</l>
<l>taṉpeyar kiḷakkuṅ kālai yeṉpeyar</l>
<l>pētaic cōḻa ṉeṉṉuñ ciṟanta</l>
<l>kātaṟ kiḻamaiyu muṭaiya ṉataṉṟalai</l>
<l>yiṉṉatōr kālai nillala</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉē varukuva ṉoḻikkavavaṟ kiṭamē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>  “While many years have passed without seeing (2) </l>
<l>anything [of him] apart from hearing a bit, (1)</l>
<l>even though he is a lord who is familiar, without blemish, (3)</l>
<l>it would be difficult [for him] to turn up [here now]. ?????conduct”, (4)</l>
<l>don’t take up such doubt, you men of rare knowledge. (5)</l>
<l>He is without reproach, sweet, in friendship bound [to me]. (6)</l>
<l>He won’t want a lie that comes to get [his] fame lost. (7)</l>
<l>At the time his name rests, my name (8)</l>
<l>says Pētai Cōḻaṉ. (9a-c)</l>
<l>He has a right to [my] exulted love. On top of that, (9d-10)</l>
<l>at [this] time that is not pleasant he won’t stay [away]. (11)</l>
<l>He will come right now. May a place be kept for him. (12)</l>
</lg>
